revenge on the FBI.

00:08.842 --> 00:12.213
What are you proposing?
You raid that money
before the FBI does.

00:12.246 --> 00:13.747
We'll do all the work
for you.

00:13.781 --> 00:15.983
Have you guys figured out
where the cash is hiding

00:16.016 --> 00:17.551
in your nightclub?

00:17.585 --> 00:20.688
Well, you certainly can't be
going into this raid blind.

00:20.721 --> 00:23.324
All we know is that
half a million dollars

00:23.357 --> 00:25.659
