somewhere inside.

00:25.693 --> 00:28.162
You won't last one hour
without getting read.

00:28.196 --> 00:29.763
Not if you help me look right.

00:29.797 --> 00:31.565
If I help you
and you pull this off,

00:31.599 --> 00:33.234
I get 10% of whatever
you're stealin' from that club.

00:33.267 --> 00:34.435
Deal.

