[ Speaking Spanish ]

00:39.940 --> 00:41.375
[ Shouting in Spanish ]

00:42.576 --> 00:44.178
If he's a lying
sack of shit,

00:44.212 --> 00:45.846
she can figure it out
without your help.

00:45.879 --> 00:48.449
We are stealing this money,
we're giving it to Lashever,

00:48.482 --> 00:50.618
then we're going to
pick up Jacob.

00:50.651 --> 00:53.287
We searched everywhere, sir,
but there was no money.

00:53.321 --> 00:54.688
It's okay, boys.

00:54.722 --> 00:56.890
You learned a very
valuable lesson.

00:56.924 --> 00:59.893
Next time, maybe you'll accept
guidance from your superiors.

00:59.927 --> 01:03.063
In the meantime, I hear
they're hiring mall cops

01:03.097 --> 01:04.765
